tmt><resp>HGV</resp></respStmt><item>Record last modified</item></change><change n="meta.15656"><date>2008-08-15</date><respStmt><resp>IDP</resp></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>III/IVspc</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r,ctr" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>χαῖρε, κύριέ μου ἄδελφε Σαραπόδωρε, 

    <lb n="2"/>Ἀπολλώνιός σε <choice><corr>προσαγορεύω</corr><sic>προσαγορευωι</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐπιστολὴν Ἀνδρομάχου ἔπεμψά σοι 

    <lb n="4"/>ὅπως ἀναδῷς καὶ τὴν ἀντιγραφὴν 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐν τάχει <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice> πέμψῃς. ἡ δὲ ἀξίωσις 

    <lb n="6"/>αὐτοῦ περὶ τοῦ τηρηθῆναι αὐ-

    <lb n="7"/>τῷ το ψήφισμα τῆς ἀναδοχῆς τῆ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="8"/>γυμνασιαρχ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ία</supplied>ς, καὶ εἰ μὲν οἷόν τε 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐστίν, <subst><add place="inline">ἃς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">τ</del>ας</del></subst> ἐκ περισσοῦ ἡμέρας ἠναγ-

    <lb n="10"/>κάσθη ποιῆσα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι π</supplied>έρυσι, παραδεχ<g type="apostrophe"/>θῆ-

    <lb n="11"/>ναι αὐτῶ εἰς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τὰς </supplied><choice><corr><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐ</supplied>πετείους</corr><sic><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>φετι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ους</unclear></sic></choice> μὴ ὀκνή-

    <lb n="12"/>σῃς. εἰ δὲ μή γε, <choice><corr>καὶ ἂν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> ἀπὸ τοῦ νῦν 

    <lb n="13"/>τηρηθῆναι τὸ ψήφισμα. τοῦτο 

    <lb n="14"/>γὰρ καὶ δικαιότατον. ὁ Ἀχιλλεὺς περὶ 

    <lb n="15"/>τοῦ οἴνου οὐδὲν οὔτε ἐνήργησεν 

    <lb n="16"/>οὔτε ἀπῄτησεν. ἐδόκει δὲ χαράσσεσ-

    <lb n="17"/>θαι ἐπὶ τούτῳ. ἡ τιμὴ τοῦ οἴνου 

    <lb n="18"/>ἐνταῦθα πάν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">υ</unclear> ἐν <choice><corr>καθυφέσει</corr><sic>κατυφεσει</sic></choice> ἐστιν. 

    <lb n="19"/>μέχρι γὰρ <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> <num value="1000">Α</num> καὶ <num value="900">ϡ</num> τυγχάνει, ὥστε, 

    <lb n="20"/>εἰ δύνατόν σοί ἐστιν Ἀλέξανδρον 

    <lb n="21"/>τὸν Ἀκωρείτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">η</supplied>ν ἀξιῶσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αι</supplied> ὅπως 

    <lb n="22"/>διὰ πλοίου αὐτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῦ</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>ήσῃ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ι ἐνε-

    <lb n="23"/>χθῆναι <choice><corr>καὶ ἂν</corr><sic>κ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αν</unclear></sic></choice> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὅ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>ο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>  <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>ὕρῃς 

    <lb n="24"/>εἰς ἃ γράφεις, <add place="supralinear">πο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ίη</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>ον</add>. ο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἱ</supplied> μέντοι Ἀντινο<hi rend="diaeresis">ϊ</hi>τι-

    <lb n="25"/>κοὶ ἐκδοχεῖς ἐ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">π</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>άξαντό μοι ὅτι, 

    <lb n="26"/>ἢ συνωνούμεθα τὰ σὰ τῆς αὐτῆς 

    <lb n="27"/>τιμῆς ἢ ἀποφέρομεν τῷ ἀδελ-

    <lb n="28"/>φῷ σου αὐτά. τοὺς τάπητας ἐξέ-

    <lb n="29"/>δωκα. ὁ γὰρ <choice><corr>σημειογράφος</corr><sic>σ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ημ</unclear>ιογραφος</sic></choice> οὐκ ἔ-

    <lb n="30"/>δωκέν μοι τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ά</supplied>πητα. <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὑπ</unclear>έσχετο 

    <lb n="31"/>μέντοι δώσ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>ν μοι <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="9">θ</num><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/> καινοῦ. 

    <lb n="32"/>εἰδέναι μέν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>οι ὀφείλε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ις</unclear> ὅτι 

    <lb n="33"/>προσελθεῖν <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear> δεῖ ἕνεκεν τῆς ἐκ-

    <lb n="34"/>κλήτου πρὸ τ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῆ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> προθεσμίας κατὰ 

    <lb n="35"/>τὸ διάταγμα. <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἔ</supplied>στιν τῆς οὐσιακῆ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="36"/>ἐπιτροπῆς ὀφφικιάλιος ἐνθάδε 

    <lb n="37"/>ζητῶν πρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">όσ</supplied>τιμον ἐκκλήτων, 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="r,ms" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="38" rend="perpendicular"/> ὃς καὶ <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice> ἕνεκεν τῆς τότε πρὸς τὸν οὐσιακ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὸ</unclear>ν περὶ <expan>χειρογρ<ex cert="high">αφ  </ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">ταλάντων</ex></expan> <num value="6">ϛ</num> καὶ μέχρι νῦν 

    <lb n="39" rend="perpendicular"/> πρὸς αὐτὸν οὐδέπω οὐδὲν ἐπράξαμεν, ἐὰν δέ τι καινότερον πραχθῇ, δηλωθήσεταί σοι. 

    <lb n="39/40"/><note lang="en" anchored="yes" place="not specified">Writing perpendicular to main text</note> ἀσπάζεταί 

    <lb n="40" rend="perpendicular"/> σε τὰ τεκνία ἡμῶν καὶ ἡ μήτηρ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αὐτῶ</unclear>ν καὶ οἱ ἡμῶν πάντες. ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι, κύριέ μου. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="41"/>Σαραποδώρωι  <figure><figDesc>drawing</figDesc></figure>  ἐξηγητῇ 

    <lb n="42"/><expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> Ἀ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">πο</unclear>λλωνίου. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.15656" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.15656" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" precision="low" notBefore="0308" notAfter="0312">ca. 308 - 312</date></p></div><div n="meta.15656" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL VIII, S. 271.</p></div><div n="meta.15656" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.15656" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">49</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3507</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">15656</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">49</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3507</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;49;3507" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.15656" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">271</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.15656" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.15656" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot"